headline.main: PRINCETON WHIGS END 200TH YEAR; Debating Society No Longer Beset by Strife

results.snippet: PRINCETON, N.J., April 10, -- The American Whig-Cliosophic Society at Princeton University, believed to be the world's oldest collegiate debating and public affairs organization, is celebrating its 200th anniversary.

byline.original: Special to The New York Times
